As I was forced to work from home and look after two young children , it is becoming increasingly difficult , if not impossible , to get the various things I need done at once .
Somehow managing to get up from the couch and breakfast , I got on the phone with Dom , a lifelong Los Angeles-area comic stripist who lives and works as an editor in one of the comic magazines .
Although he is never terribly pleasant to the touch , he is evident both in the way he treats me and in the way he treats his audience .
